node.title: Police search for missing man in Christchurch
node.description: Christchurch police are searching for a man who has not returned home from a bike ride this morning.
node.content:
["Christchurch police are searching for a man who has not returned home from a bike ride this morning.", "", "
Murray Bennett, 67. Photo: Supplied / NZ Police
", "Police said Murray Bennett, 67, left his home in Hillsborough shortly after 11am but has not returned as expected.", "He was wearing a long-sleeved blue and white checked shirt and blue shorts, with a red and black bike helmet.", "Murray had some health concerns and there were concerns for his welfare, police said.", "Anyone who thinks they may have seen Murray since late this morning is asked to get in touch with police by calling 105 and quote event number P049456901."]
